CouchDB server adaptor for SproutCore. Includes updated SC.Server, SC.RestServer, and SC.RailsServer implementations.

*NOTE*: Overrides built-in SproutCore implementations of SC.Server, SC.RestServer, and SC.RailsServer.

Usage:

  $ sc-install onitunes-couchdb
  
  Then edit sc-config:
  
    c[:required] = [:sproutcore, :'onitunes-couchdb']
    
  ...and restart sc-server.